<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>15</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Thangthat tuah u, Lei le van sertu Bawi kan Siang pa hrang, Ka thlarau
 thangthat tuah, na damnak le tlannak a si, A theimi nih a biakinn naih
 chin ko u, Hmun khat ah thangthat ti u si.

[V2]
 Thangthat tuah u, Zeizong vialte uktu Bawipa a si! A thla tangah him
 tein an huh phenh i an cawm ko, Na herh vialte ti le rawl zong Bawipa
 nih, An pek lengmang, na hngal lo maw?

[V3]
 Thangthat tuah u, Nanmah bawmtu le hupphengtu Bawi cu, A zaangfah le
 velngeihnak in nan mah an zohkhenh hna, Ruat than tuah u, Pathian he
 hawikomhnak cu, Zeitluk a that kha nan hngalh lai!.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<title>BAWI CUNGNUNG BIK THANGTHAT U CH15</title>
</song>